Tetris Clone
Author: Andrew Chao
4/1/2012

Files
- tetris.py
- constants.py
- Board.py
- Piece.py

Built with
- Python 3.2
- Pygame 1.9.2a0

*********************************************************************************
INSTRUCTIONS

Run tetris.py to start the game. Please make sure you have pygame installed.

There are 10 levels

